cast.overview: The Swedish Björn Borg and the American John McEnroe, the best tennis players in the world, maintain a legendary duel during the 1980 Wimbledon tournament.
cast.title: Borg vs McEnroe

details.biography:
Jackson Gann is the young and extremely talented American actor who has already achieved huge landmarks in his acting career. Recently, he is known for his appearance in the television drama with a mysterious story line, The Alienist.

Furthermore, at a very young age, he has gained mainstream recognition already in his career from different appearances in movies and television dramas. His exceptional skills in acting have gained himself many adorers and lovers from the cinematic universe audience. Starting his journey from the year 2014 as Kevin in a short movie. He is currently playing in the Netflix series You.

- IMDb Mini Biography By: yusufpiskin
details.name: Jackson Gann
